('LIST-004-A Internal Audit Schedule', 'List', 'Managed digitally within the Xyreg Audit Management module. The audit schedule is maintained from Quality Operations > Audits with automated frequency tracking and coverage analysis.'),
('LIST-005-A Training Matrix', 'List', 'Managed digitally within the Xyreg Training Management module. The training matrix showing role-based training requirements and completion status is accessible from Settings > Training.'),
('LIST-009-C Approved Supplier List (ASL)', 'List', 'Managed digitally within the Xyreg Supplier Management module. The ASL is maintained from Quality Operations > Suppliers showing qualification status, approved materials/services, and re-evaluation dates.'),
('LIST-012-B CAPA Log', 'List', 'Managed digitally within the Xyreg CAPA module. The CAPA log with status tracking, trending, and metrics is accessible from Quality Operations > CAPA dashboard.'),
('LIST-013-A Complaint Log', 'List', 'Managed digitally within the Xyreg Complaints module. The complaint log with trending, product analysis, and regulatory reporting status is accessible from Quality Operations > Complaints dashboard.'),
